{
  "texts": [
    "**Resources Provided:** -**Minecraft Game Environment:** `{env}-**Agent Experience Records:** `{experience}-**Current Agent States:** `{agent state}-**List of Available Agents:** `{free agent}-**List of Tasks:** `{tasks}* *Assignment Objective:** You are to match tasks with suitable agents from the available list and produce a series of task-assignment JSON objects.",
    "The JSON format should be as follows: ```json { \"reason\": \"Explanation of the selection process, detailing why the agent is fit for the task based on their current state and held items.",
    "\", \"task_id\": \"The ID of the selected task.",
    "\", \"agent\": \"Names of agents assigned to the task.\"",
    "} ``* *Key Instructions:** -Provide a step-by-step reasoning for each task assignment."
  ]
